                             -*- text -*-

                            HOW TO INSTALL

To compile, just run 

    make

To install in /usr/local, run 

    make install

as root. 

You will need the following packages on Ubuntu, or similar ones on
your system:

    libpcap0.8         The pcap library (you NEED 0.8!)
    libpcap0.8-dev     Headers for pcap
    libghc6-mtl-dev    Monad transformer library

To install in some other directory, run

    make install PREFIX=/some/other/directory        

To compile the tests, run

    make test
        
